I stumble to my car,

00:00:31.930 --> 00:00:34.900 align:middle line:84%
reaching for that granola bar
stashed in the center console

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:38.460 align:middle line:84%
because, after all, I never
leave my house without snacks.

00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:40.900 align:middle line:84%
